OL,3,CIsle of Man nurses 'prepared to
OL,4,Cstrike' over Manx Care 4% pay offer
OL,6,FNurses in the Isle of Man have voted
OL,7,Fin favour of strike action, after
OL,8,Frejecting a 4% uplift in pay proposed
OL,9,Fby Manx Care.
OL,11,FOf those who voted in a Royal College
OL,12,Fof Nursing (RCN) ballot on whether
OL,13,Fthey would consider striking, 70%
OL,14,Fagreed to to take this action.
OL,16,FManx Care offered a 4% pay uplift with
OL,17,Feffect from 1 April 2024 for staff
OL,18,Femployed at the time an agreement is
OL,19,Freached.
