OL,3,CIsle of Man nurses 'prepared to
OL,4,Cstrike' over Manx Care 4% pay offer
OL,6,FNorth West Regional Director for the
OL,7,FRCN, Simon Browes, said: "The result
OL,8,Fof this ballot speaks for itself. Our
OL,9,Fmembers do not feel like they are
OL,10,Fbeing heard and believe that taking
OL,11,Faction is necessary to bring about a
OL,12,Fresolution.
