OL,3,CIsle of Man nurses 'prepared to
OL,4,Cstrike' over Manx Care 4% pay offer
OL,6,F"The RCN has been clear since the
OL,7,Fstart of this process, that industrial
OL,8,Faction is always a last resort, but we
OL,9,Fare also clear that the skill,
OL,10,Fprofessionalism, and safety critical
OL,11,Fwork of nursing staff has historically
OL,12,Fbeen undervalued, and that patients
OL,13,Fare being put at risk due to the
OL,14,Fstaffing crisis on the Isle of Man.
