OL,3,CIsle of Man nurses 'prepared to
OL,4,Cstrike' over Manx Care 4% pay offer
OL,6,F"Whilst next steps will need to be
OL,7,Fdiscussed, the majority of our members
OL,8,Fhave made their voices clear. We are
OL,9,Fnow in a position to proceed to a
OL,10,Fstatutory ballot on industrial action,
OL,11,Fallowing our members to lawfully
OL,12,Fstrike.
OL,14,F"We are asking Manx Care to consider
OL,15,Fthis strong message and to continue
OL,16,Fnegotiations with our members."
OL,18,FManx Care has been contacted for
OL,19,Fcomment.
